    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx, that's a good start. can u expand on the \"sophisticated\" look for a global business setting? like, if someone is attending a high-level gala or a formal boardroom meeting in london, singapore, or lagos, what's the standard outfit that screams \"professional\" and \"high status\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For a high-level gala or formal boardroom meeting in any of those cities, a tailored suit in a neutral color such as navy, black, or charcoal is a safe bet. A crisp white shirt, a slim tie, and high-quality dress shoes will convey a sense of sophistication. For women, a well-tailored pantsuit or a cocktail dress in a neutral color is also suitable. Avoid anything too flashy or revealing, as it may be misinterpreted in a conservative culture. A classic watch, a simple yet elegant piece of jewelry, and a quality handbag or briefcase will complete the professional look.",
